  "body": "I see many OSS repos use a different coding style from the scalafmt default style\r\n\r\n* --maxColumn 100 (scala.js + scalafmt are the only repos I've seen look nicely with 80 character limit)\r\n* --continuationIndentCallSite 2\r\n* --assumeStdLibStripMargin false"
